<p><strong>Name:</strong> Dr. [REDACTED] Henderson</p>
<p><strong>Security Clearance:</strong> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Level 3</span> N/A</p>
<p><strong>Role:</strong> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Psychologist at Site-43.</span> N/A</p>
<p><strong>Current Status:</strong> Dead</p>
<p><strong>Objects Related to Dr. Henderson and his Person:</strong></p>
<p><a href="/scp-2238">SCP-2238</a><br />
<a href="/scp-2891">SCP-2891</a><br />
<a href="/scp-2893">SCP-2893</a><br />
