<a href="/scp-4136">SCP-4136</a></p>
<p><strong>Reports filed by Dr. Henderson:</strong></p>
<p><a href="/green-day">Green Day</a><br />
<a href="/green-day-ii">Green Day II</a><br />
<a href="/yellow-plumbers">Yellow Plumbers</a><br />
<a href="/sands-of-time">Sands Of Time</a></p>
